name: Worthless billions #4
description: The current crisis has cemented tech billionaires’ status as masters of the universe. This is a series of characters that have made billions during the pandemic, increasing their ‘worth’, for whatever that means. As of today, April 29th, 2021, Zuckerberg’s net worth is 118.8 billion USD according to Forbes. 118 pieces available, each one representing one billion of this worth, that in the end... are worthless.
